@page "/returns"

<PageTitle>Returns &amp; Refunds — Katie's Garden</PageTitle>

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">

    <div role="alert" class="alert alert-warning mb-8">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
        </svg>
        <div>
            <p class="font-semibold">REQUIRES REVIEW</p>
            <p class="text-sm">This policy is a placeholder and must be reviewed and approved by Katie or a qualified legal adviser before the site goes live.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-semibold text-base-content mb-2">Returns &amp; Refunds</h1>
    <p class="text-base-content/50 text-sm mb-8">Last updated: @DateTime.UtcNow.ToString("MMMM yyyy")</p>

    <div class="prose prose-stone max-w-none">

        <h2>Our commitment</h2>
        <p>We want you to be completely happy with your purchase from Katie's Garden. If something isn't right, please get in touch and we'll do our best to make it right.</p>

        <h2>Plants and perishable goods</h2>
        <p>Because plants are living things, we cannot accept returns on healthy plants that have been correctly cared for after purchase. However, if a plant arrives in poor condition or is clearly not as described, please contact us within <strong>48 hours</strong> with a photo and we will offer a replacement or full refund.</p>

        <h2>Woodwork and handmade items</h2>
        <p>Handmade items (bug houses, planters, garden furniture) may be returned within <strong>14 days</strong> if they are unused and in their original condition. Please contact us before returning any item.</p>
        <p>As these are bespoke, handmade items, minor natural variations in wood grain and finish are not considered defects.</p>

        <h2>Damaged or incorrect items</h2>
        <p>If your order arrives damaged or you receive the wrong item, please contact us within <strong>48 hours</strong> of collection or delivery. We will arrange a replacement or refund at no cost to you.</p>

        <h2>How to request a return or refund</h2>
        <p>Email <a href="mailto:team@katiesgarden.uk">team@katiesgarden.uk</a> with your order number and a description of the issue. We aim to respond within 2 business days.</p>

        <h2>Refunds</h2>
        <p>Approved refunds will be processed to your original payment method via Stripe within 5–10 business days.</p>

        <h2>Your statutory rights</h2>
        <p>These terms do not affect your statutory rights under the Consumer Rights Act 2015. UK consumers have the right to goods that are of satisfactory quality, fit for purpose, and as described.</p>

    </div>
</div>
